_sText:
Some map I put together throughout a few days, mainly just did it for fun so it isn't super detailed or anything and I didn't even originally plan to publish it to gamebanana but a few of my friends enjoyed running it so I figured I would clean it up a little and publish it here for others to play, I have added checkpoints but just keep in mind the whole map is intended to be a relatively easy linear strafe map.

Map is Multiple themes.
